* Change the job running code to be resilient to Android 8+ background restrictions.
* Bump the minimum version to API 26 in order to dump a bunch of old API calls.

v1.3 (1011)

* Build with and target Android 12 due to an issue setting alarms.

v1.3 (1010)

crond has been forked from upstream, with the following new features.

* Set exact alarms on Android 23+
* Show crond.log in the app.
* Add support for some useful-for-debugging cron expressions.
  @enable triggers when crond is enabled.
  @change triggers when the crontab is detected as having changed.
  @reboot triggers when the device boots.
* Allow crond to run without root.

Note that new strings were added, so non-English translations will have issues.
